IActorEventPublisher<TIActorEvents> IActorEventPublisher(Of TIActorEvents) Interface

In this Article

Edit

Represents publisher of actor events. Publishers of actor events must implement this interface

Syntax

Declaration

public interface IActorEventPublisher<TIActorEvents> : IActorEventPublisher where TIActorEvents : IActorEventsPublic Interface IActorEventPublisher(Of TIActorEvents As IActorEvents)
    Inherits IActorEventPublisher

Type Parameters

TIActorEvents

Actor event interface type derived from IActorEvents.

Details

Assembly
